OL,3,C'I want to see some money': Lord Sugar
OL,4,Crevives Amstrad brand with marketing
OL,5,Cfirm
OL,7,Fis to revive his famous brand Amstrad
OL,8,Fwith the launch of a new digital
OL,9,Fmarketing company led by his grandson,
OL,10,F17 years after selling the business to
OL,11,FSky.
OL,13,FThe business mogul, who fronts BBC One
OL,14,Freality series The Apprentice, bought
OL,15,Fback the rights to the household brand
OL,16,Fname for new agency Amstrad Digital.
