OL,3,C'I want to see some money': Lord Sugar
OL,4,Crevives Amstrad brand with marketing
OL,5,Cfirm
OL,7,FLord Sugar criticised the
OL,8,F"belligerent" old management at Sky,
OL,9,Fprior to it being taken over by US
OL,10,Fmedia giant Comcast in 2018, for not
OL,11,Fallowing him to buy back the name.
OL,13,F"I had always asked, since 2007, to
OL,14,Fhave it back because I want to give it
OL,15,Fdown to the family to use in their
OL,16,Fbusiness," he said.
