OL,3,C'I want to see some money': Lord Sugar
OL,4,Crevives Amstrad brand with marketing
OL,5,Cfirm
OL,7,FThe businessman founded electronics
OL,8,Fcompany Amstrad in 1968, at the age of
OL,9,F21, selling audio and computer
OL,10,Fequipment before making the first
OL,11,Frange of Sky receivers and dishes.
OL,13,FAmstrad was eventually sold to the
OL,14,Fbroadcasting giant for #125 million,
OL,15,Fwhich still uses the software but not
OL,16,Fthe brand name.
