OL,3,C'I want to see some money': Lord Sugar
OL,4,Crevives Amstrad brand with marketing
OL,5,Cfirm
OL,7,FLord Sugar's grandson Joe Baron and
OL,8,FTom D'Arcy, who both worked at rival
OL,9,Fdigital marketing agency Climb Online,
OL,10,Fwill head up the new performance
OL,11,Fmarketing agency.
OL,13,FClimb Online was launched by The
OL,14,FApprentice winner Mark Wright with the
OL,15,Finvestment of Lord Sugar, and sold in
OL,16,F2022 for a reported #10 million.
OL,18,F"They've got the brand name, that in
OL,19,Fitself is worth a fortune, and they've
OL,20,Fgot to exploit it. And I want to see
OL,21,Fsome money," Lord Sugar said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/6
