OL,3,C'I want to see some money': Lord Sugar
OL,4,Crevives Amstrad brand with marketing
OL,5,Cfirm
OL,7,FHe also criticised working from home
OL,8,Fculture, brought about by the Covid
OL,9,Fpandemic, adding: "These two lads are
OL,10,Fnot going to sit in their pyjamas
OL,11,Fworking from home, they've got to get
OL,12,Fout there and do some business."
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Lord Sugar acknowledged
OL,15,Ftelevision advertising has "suffered
OL,16,Fbadly", amid reports the sector has
OL,17,Ffaced tougher conditions in recent
OL,18,Fyears due to rising costs and shifting
OL,19,Fconsumer viewing habits.
