OL,3,C'I want to see some money': Lord Sugar
OL,4,Crevives Amstrad brand with marketing
OL,5,Cfirm
OL,7,F"TV companies have cut back
OL,8,Ftremendously, and the reason for that
OL,9,Fis because the power of television
OL,10,Fadvertising is not as big as it was,"
OL,11,Fhe added.
OL,13,F"It is now digital marketing, digital
OL,14,Fadvertising and social media that are
OL,15,Factually pulling in sales."
